through the divorce.

346
00:27:59,088 --> 00:28:00,555
I had my pride.

347
00:28:02,755 --> 00:28:04,088
He didn’t love me.

348
00:28:06,288 --> 00:28:07,400
He only loved his son.

349
00:28:11,333 --> 00:28:12,511
He was an alcoholic,

350
00:28:15,355 --> 00:28:17,600
