Even on that night,
he came over to visit Wang.

352
00:28:26,933 --> 00:28:28,533
It was after he put our son to bed

353
00:28:30,977 --> 00:28:36,933
and after we started drinking that I told him...

354
00:28:39,555 --> 00:28:41,222
I told him.

355
00:28:44,444 --> 00:28:46,777
I knew he wasn’t like this because of me.

356
00:28:49,977 --> 00:28:51,133
I told him.

